The Good, the Bad, the Weird;;83;;82;;R;;In 1930s Manchuria, an encounter on a train triggers an epic crusade for a treasure map, prompting a marathon chase in hot pursuit of the loot. Do-won, "The Good", is a bounty hunter, out to track down Chang-yee, "The Bad", a charismatic hit man attempting to steal the map from a military official. However, the ruthless Tae-goo puts a hitch in both their plans when he secures the map for himself.;;Action,Western;;Kim Jee-woon;;2008;;Song Kang-ho,Lee Byung-hun,Jung Woo-sung,Ryu Seung-soo,Yoon Je-moon,Song Young-chang,Son Byeong-ho,Oh Dal-su;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_good_the_bad_the_weird